  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enable 240 people with disabilities in Sri Lanka</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Those with disabilities in Sri Lanka continue to face poverty and hardship due to stigma, lack of community support and infrastructure.  Prithipura Communities provides a home, rehabilitation, education and work opportunities to 240 children and adults with disabilities with little or no family support, across 4 locations in Sri Lanka.  This project will contribute towards the salaries of 50 experienced carers and teachers.</narrative>
